text.__SUMMARY__: Prunus malayana is a species of plant in the family Rosaceae. It is a tree endemic to Peninsular Malaysia.
text.References: Kalkman, C. (1998). "Prunus malayana". The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. IUCN. 1998: e.T31777A9653102. doi:10.2305/IUCN.UK.1998.RLTS.T31777A9653102.en. Retrieved 22 December 2017.
